<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Http_Client includes the full URI in the request.  For instance, a request may look like:</p>

<pre class="literal">
GET <a href="https://www.website.com/path?key=value">https://www.website.com/path?key=value</a> HTTP/1.1
</pre>

<p>Instead of:</p>

<pre class="literal">
GET /path?key=value HTTP/1.1
</pre>

<p>The attached patch fixes this.</p>

    </div>
